nodes.name: buyTickets
nodes.text: functionbuyTickets(uint256ticketAmount)externalpayable{require(startTime<=block.timestamp,"Project not yet launched");require(endTime>=block.timestamp,"Project already finished");require(ticketCount+ticketAmount<=maximumTicketCount,"Ticket limit reached");if(msg.sender!=owner()){require(msg.value>=ticketPrice*ticketAmount,"Not enough funds available");}myTicketCount[msg.sender][lotteryIndex]=myTicketCount[msg.sender][lotteryIndex]+ticketAmount;for(uint256x=0;x<ticketAmount;x++){ticketCount=ticketCount+1;myTickets[msg.sender][lotteryIndex].push(ticketCount);ticketHolders.push(msg.sender);}}
